wn out of the sky July 17 by a surface-to-air missile, killing all 298 passengers and crew. The UN resolution demanded that all military activities, including by armed groups, be "immediately ceased in the immediate area surrounding the crash site to allow for security and safety of the international investigation."  AFP PHOTO / Timothy A. CLARY";s:17:"created_timestamp";i:1405944994;s:9:"copyright";s:0:"";s:12:"focal_length";i:0;s:3:"iso";i:0;s:13:"shutter_speed";i:0;s:5:"title";s:27:"UN-SECURITY COUNCIL-UKRAINE";s:11:"orientation";i:0;}}'),
